Yamagishi, 1993: 812 (original description); 
<bibRefCitation author="Kononova, SV" journalOrPublisher="Tovarishchestvo Nauchnykh Izdanii KMK, Saint Petersburg" pageId="9" pageNumber="108" year="2008">Kononova and Kozlov 2008</bibRefCitation>
